{"tid":595014,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"茶狼，做乜有人排隊","createTime":"2018-03-16T10:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T17:21:32.000Z","uid":135896,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f261d01b94feb3f91aa767c035c1c3eea54f0e8","tid":595014,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"飲過兩次都冇乜特別，個芝士奶蓋完全食唔出有芝士味，根本就係三花淡奶，啲茶又唔係特別香，去茶樓飲開茶叫壺香片鐵觀音自己加d糖根本就一樣，香港土炮扮台灣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc6261abe94065fded3ba778b890ce7e157d377","tid":595014,"uid":102745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"贏gimmick囉<br />\nd人見到pop up store就覺得機會難逢<br />\n加上食正芝士奶蓋條水<br />\n但其實我覺得芝士奶蓋除左鹹過普通奶蓋少少之外都會乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7408235d3512d8c8cd98d3f197c7fc339c1f4920","tid":595014,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"美心集團"},{"pid":"9e4febbc3e7468a072b2befd1af94f82fe9d93bb","tid":595014,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7408235d3512d8c8cd98d3f197c7fc339c1f4920","tid":595014,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"美心集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"最反感係佢扮台灣, 香港咁大個集團做生意淨係識跟，有少少創意得唔得，我第一次飲完果次，知道係美心，身為香港人覺得好丑"},{"pid":"95fcdaf06ddf36b8a958aa83b2c65794e45fd5a7","tid":595014,"uid":81609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為你改國歌添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3054bd3c804974e94345569a4637f08cac3d10","tid":595014,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fcdaf06ddf36b8a958aa83b2c65794e45fd5a7","tid":595014,"uid":81609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為你改國歌添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />